{"tid":1018501,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"依家連中學生都講蝗語 忍唔住屌鳩佢地","createTime":"2019-02-12T09:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T11:53:10.000Z","uid":96460,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"074ae6ad448b1fc5c04196b3d7fa9a491199d13b","tid":1018501,"uid":96460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"今日搭巴士  成班中學生係度大大聲講蝗語 又開到game 聲大一大<br />\n<br />\n開頭都係啤下佢地 等佢地知驚<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母 原來佢地大部分識講廣東話 係就其中一個肥仔 講蝗語<br />\n<br />\n講咩操你媽個B 咁 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住用純正廣東粗口屌鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;屌你老母 嘈撚夠未呀 呢度香港黎架 講廣東話啦&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地即刻靜哂  最尾車都唔敢落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 本身都唔想幫人教仔 純粹忍唔緊  睇唔過眼後生一代咁唔尊重本地文化"},{"pid":"45efae92b97bb7e97c12ded5ee210d7a4c4f4fd9","tid":1018501,"uid":39496,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔信你"},{"pid":"5f32ced8c9a90c893446608ed33f44384b3b3437","tid":1018501,"uid":215951,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79da817d5d7683c15a61b3486937f24b49def2e8","tid":1018501,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"之前聽過話有學校如果聽到學生講廣東話，會罰佢地<br />\n係咪真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f994b39bf05bbd60b35ef72a74acab37e4786dd2","tid":1018501,"uid":96460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f32ced8c9a90c893446608ed33f44384b3b3437",